,"tid":229443,"uid":60279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T09:32:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我好耐之前都試過，<br />\n果時一家五口想去大阪<br />\ntotal 訂左17張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n果時一直show error 話交易不成功 (有cap圖）<br />\n所以無為意，一直keep 住買<br />\n<br />\n買買下價錢又貴左<br />\n之後買果幾張係第2d 日子<br />\n起初cs都話唔係double booking 退唔到<br />\n但我老豆老母keep 住日日打幾次去屌鳩佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後嘈到大部分cs 都知我地係麻煩友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n經過十日左右，有負責人話可以退了<br />\n<br />\n但退錢要8個星期，姐係要找左卡數先<br />\n找左既卡數變左deposit 係張卡入面<br />\n係唔可以攞返錢出黎用<br />\n你只有之後碌左佢<br />\n<br />\n從此之後，我每次一見到呢d 網上交易不成功都即打去card centre<br />\n買個教訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nNO LA<br />\nCREDIT CARD入面既錢可以要求囉番出SAVING<br />\n不過要囉曬, 唔可以囉一半唔囉一半"},{"pid":"43fbe10927ce1221640e79e9f6d5a43ab157435f","tid":229443,"uid":57675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T10:06:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解會願意比7千坐uo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n總要有on9 幫下呢間西野既</blockquote><br />\n可能幫埋人訂 訂好多張呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cec2dc46aa10d94b1d981e03fc9d154f16a45951","tid":229443,"uid":43819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T10:23:19.000Z","msg":"原本改日期時間9點果班再補$900，5點半點果班補$500<br />\n咁我改9點果班，過左個零月check下班機佢偷偷地將班機更左做5點9，到出發前一星期先通知你班機改早左，<br />\n咁算唔算比佢食夾棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我比多左錢只係遲左15分鐘走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"